title: 24 Season 3 Disc 3
description:
Jack Bauer, Director of Field Ops for the Counter-Terrorist Unit of Los Angeles, races against the clock to subvert terrorist plots and save his nation from ultimate disaster. - IMDB

I've gotten a few comments asking why I disappeared after posting these files.  

1.  I have not disappeared, but sometimes do not spend my entire month uploading files

2.  My ISP has been sending me multiple emails regarding the amount of bandwidth I am consuming on the upstream, and have gone so far as to ask if I was hosting a web site from my computer.  I had to take a break in order to keep my service on.

3.  Every few weeks I end up in the hospital due to my medical condition.  I am not going to go into any more detail regarding that.

If you can't deal with these small hold-ups, then don't begin downloading.  However, if you are patient, you will see all files will be fully seeded
